<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="objectType">Wall</rs> of  doorway to stage room.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Below <xref type="inscription" n="1754" href="080018">8.18</xref>, on another smoothed area. There are apparent traces of previous lettering which has been erased. The second line of script is far shallower, and is cut on the very edge of the smoothed area.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Rough, lunate lettering, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05</measure>
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0001" notAfter="0600">First  to sixth century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">context</rs>)</p>
</div>
