<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>Of Bassos. ...? to the Lord.</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>One of the group of inscriptions, apparently by performers, at the doorways of the rooms on the stage front:  <xref type="inscription" n="698" href="080008">8.8</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="699" href="080009">8.9</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="700" href="080104">8.104</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1567" href="080015">8.15</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1707" href="080016">8.16</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1716" href="080017">8.17</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1754" href="080018">8.18</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1755" href="080019">8.19</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1759" href="080020">8.20</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1760" href="080021">8.21</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1895" href="080022">8.22</xref>. See <bibl n="PPA">Roueché, <title>PPA</title>, pp. 15-25.</bibl>.</p>


</div>
